        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2021790754" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer422869567717570006">This book is filled with signature McPhee writing. Concise, wise, measured. Great stuff. But I really struggled to get through this book. He has a way of using common language to describe quite technical and ungraspable concepts, so the end result is you just feel like you&apos;re going insane. I could grab 20 great paragraphs from this book, but I never want to look at the entirety ever again.</span>
  <span id="freeText422869567717570006" style="display:none">This book is filled with signature McPhee writing. Concise, wise, measured. Great stuff. But I really struggled to get through this book. He has a way of using common language to describe quite technical and ungraspable concepts, so the end result is you just feel like you're going insane. I could grab 20 great paragraphs from this book, but I never want to look at the entirety ever again.</span>
