 century before Magellan. Also concealed was how the Chinese colonized America before the Europeans &amp; transplanted in America &amp; other countries the principal economic crops that have fed &amp; clothed the world.\n\nUnveiling incontrovertible evidence of these astonishing voyages, &quot;1421&quot; rewrites our understanding of history. Our knowledge of world exploration as it\'s been commonly accepted for centuries must now be reconceived due to this landmark work of historical investigation.<\/span>\n  <a data-text-id=\"7889990586203008707\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"swapContent(\$(this));; return false;\">...more<\/a>\n\n    <\/div>\n\n      <div class=\'wtrButtonContainer wtrSignedOut\' id=\'22_book_4813\'>\n<div class=\'wtrUp wtrLeft\'>\n<form action=\"/shelf/add_to_shelf\" accept-charset=\"UTF-8\" method=\"post\"><input name=\"utf8\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"&#x2713;\" /><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"authenticity_token\" value=\"91baRBjgbmFDnVERij8Q75nuUIADogeTYg/Aj4Bxpcu+zSPUi/PdWU//sjf/v3yZ9HBSFE2Zl6gWkZUhD1k/oQ==\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"book_id\" id=\"book_id\" value=\"4813\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"name\" id=\"name\" value=\"to-read\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"unique_id\" id=\"unique_id\" value=\"22_book_4813\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"wtr_new\" id=\"wtr_new\" value=\"true\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"from_choice\" id=\"from_choice\" value=\"false\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"from_home_module\" id=\"from_home_module\" value=\"false\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"ref\" id=\"ref\" value=\"\" class=\"wtrLeftUpRef\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"existing_review\" id=\"existing_review\" value=\"false\" class=\"wtrExisting\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"book_origin\" id=\"book_origin\" value=\"related_works\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"page_url\" id=\"page_url\" value=\"/book/show/3130352-basin-and-range\" />\n<button class=\'wtrToRead\' type=\'submit\'>\n<span class=\'progressTrigger\'>Wa